 《TimeSplitters》开发商分享取消重启的片段https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/timesplitters-developer-shares-footage-of-cancelled-reboot-3597464?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=timesplitters-developer-shares-footage-of-cancelled-重启Ali ShutlerWed, 06 Mar 2024 11:31:41 +0000 Gaming NewsNewsPCPS5xbox series x/shttps://www.nme.com/?p=3597464 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/TimeSplitters-2-artwork.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="时间分割器2" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/TimeSplitters-2-artwork.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/TimeSplitters-2-artwork-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/TimeSplitters-2-artwork-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/TimeSplitters-2-artwork-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/TimeSplitters-2-artwork-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/TimeSplitters-2-artwork-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> Free Radical 去年 12 月被母公司 Embracer 关闭</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/timesplitters-developer-shares-footage-of-cancelled-reboot-3597464">《TimeSplitters》开发者分享取消重启的视频的帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/TimeSplitters-2-artwork.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="时间分割器2" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/TimeSplitters-2-artwork.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/TimeSplitters-2-artwork-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/TimeSplitters-2-artwork-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/TimeSplitters-2-artwork-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/TimeSplitters-2-artwork-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/TimeSplitters-2-artwork-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> Free Radical Design 的艺术主管 Rob Steptoe 分享了该工作室可能已取消的<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/timesplitters"><em>TimeSplitters</em></a>游戏的片段。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/as-dusk-falls-playstation-interview-caroline-marchal-ryan-nolan-3596299">为什么 PlayStation 粉丝应该对《黄昏降临》感到兴奋</a></strong></li></ul><p>去年 12 月，<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/timesplitters-studio-officially-closing-down-3557808">Free Radical Design 被确认将立即关闭</a>，其所有者 Embracer Group 实施了激烈的重组计划。</p><p>自 2021 年工作室重新启动以来，它一直在开发第四款<em>Timesplitters</em>游戏。 “你问我们，我们听。我们一直在制定计划，让<em>TimeSplitters</em>特许经营重新焕发活力，”母公司 Embracer 当时 <a href="https://twitter.com/deepsilver/status/1395238772938264577" target="_blank" rel="noopener">表示</a>。</p><p>后续细节很少，虽然一款新的<em>TimeSplitters</em>游戏尚未正式取消，但所有开发该游戏的人都已被解雇。</p><p>然而，斯特普托在 LinkedIn 上的一篇帖子中分享了一段五分钟的视频，其中包含比赛的镜头，现已删除。该游戏正在以<em>TimeSplitters Next</em>为标题进行开发，视频拍摄于 2023 年 7 月。该视频已存档于<a href="https://streamable.com/a9kjb1" target="_blank" rel="noopener">此处</a>。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">看到一位前开发者发布了《时间分割器 2》的游戏玩法，我想我会在拥抱者核爆它之前重新上传它<a href="https://t.co/qJeYuKqtrk">pic.twitter.com/qJeYuKqtrk</a></p><p> - 扎克·普里斯 (@zac2806) <a href="https://twitter.com/zac2806/status/1764967734113079735?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024 年 3 月 5 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p> Free Radicals 关闭后，一位匿名开发者向<a href="https://freeradical.fandom.com/wiki/TimeSplitters_(2021)/Anonymous_Interview" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Free Radical Archive</a>项目透露， <em>TimeSplitters 4</em>的最初计划是创建一个带有大量微交易的“堡垒<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/fortnite">之夜克隆</a>版”。 “没有人真正想要这样，甚至我们也不想，但很长一段时间我们没有太多选择，”他们说。</p><p>他们接着表示<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/free-radical-were-working-on-a-timesplitters-2-remake-when-the-studio-was-shut-down-3560427">，开发工作在 2023 年的某个时候发生了转变，团队将重点打造《 <em>TimeSplitters 2</em>重制版》，其中</a>包含重新设计的关卡、假设式故事情节，以及原版<em>《TimeSplitters》</em>和<em>《TimeSplitters: Future Perfect》中的关卡。</em></p><p>他们声称这款游戏距离完成还有两年的时间，但“截至目前，它已被取消。”</p><p>其他消息方面，<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/warner-bros">华纳兄弟</a>表示，继<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/suicide-squad-kill-the-justice-league">《自杀小队：杀死正义联盟》</a></em> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/suicide-squad-kill-the-justice-league-hasnt-met-warner-bros-expectations-3592065">反响</a>平平后，它将<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/warner-bros-to-pivot-away-from-volatile-aaa-games-and-focus-on-live-service-3597444">从“不稳定”的 AAA 游戏转向</a>专注于直播服务和移动游戏。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/timesplitters-developer-shares-footage-of-cancelled-reboot-3597464">《TimeSplitters》开发者分享取消重启的视频的帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
